text: Georg Waldvogel (born 7 July 1961) is a German ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of West Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:People from Breisgau-Hochschwarzwald
